title: Wipro launches a 40,000-sq-ft tech innovation studio in Austin - Economic Times
content: Wipro launches a 40,000-sq-ft tech innovation studio in Austin  Economic Times
description: The studio at in the technology and research park is designed to be a productive, state-of-art collaborative space comprising 36 huddle rooms, 12 conference rooms and 330 individual think spaces, the company said in a statement.
